Build the docker image:
$ docker build . -t danlsgiga/nginx-naxsi:latest

Run the nginx compilation like this:

$ docker run --name nginx-naxsi -e NGINX_VERSION=nginx-1.11.11-1 -e OPENSSL_VERSION=openssl-1.1.0e -e NAXSI_BRANCH=master danlsgiga/nginx-naxsi

To copy the ngx_http_naxsi_module.so module:

$ docker cp nginx-naxsi:/home/builder/rpmbuild/BUILD/nginx-1.11.11/objs/ngx_http_naxsi_module.so .
